lyrics:
[Verse]
In the Andes, where the mountains rise so high
Where ancient cultures dance under the sky
Aymaras, Quechuas, with pride they sway
Their rhythmic steps pave the colorful way

[Chorus]
Cordillera, majestic, in your embrace we find
The beauty of traditions that forever bind
Bolivia, Peru, Brazil, and more
In your enchanting dances, our spirits soar
